 "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1015627, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Glory be to God whom the praise of the best orators cannot describe and the grateful worshippers cannot thank for His Bounties. And what He says is more conclusive than what we say. Glory be to God as He praised Himself. …Nor shall they compass aught of His knowledge except as He willeth. His Throne doth extend over the heavens and the earth, and He feeleth no fatigue in guarding and preserving them for He is the Most High, the Supreme (in glory).", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "SUBHAA-NAL LAZEE LAA YOHSEE MID-HATO-HUL QAAAE-LOONA WA LAA YAJZEE BE-AALAA-E-HISH SHAAKE-ROONAL A’ABE-DOONA WA HOWA KAMAA QAALA WA FAWQA MAA NAQOO-LO WAL-LAAHO KAMAA ASNAA A’LAA NAFSE-HI WA LAA YOHEE-TOONA BE-SHAIY-IN MIN I’LME-HI ILLAA BE-MAA SHAAA-A WASE-A’ KURSEE-YO-HUS SAMAA-WAATE WAL ARZA WA LAA YAOODO-HU HIFZO-HOMAA WA HOWAL A’LIY-YUL A’ZEEMO.", "ArabicText1": "سُبْحَانَ الَّذِيْ لَا يُحْصِيْ مِدْحَتَهُ الْقَاۗئِلُوْنَ وَلَا يَجْزِيْ بِآلَائِهِ الشَّاكِرُوْنَ الْعَابِدُوْنَ 