t19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1011469, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Glory be to Allah; the Shaper of breathes. Glory be to Allah, the Fashioner. Glory be to Allah, the Creator of all pairs. Glory be to Allah, the Maker of darkness and light. Glory be to Allah the Causer the grain and the stone to germinate. Glory be to Allah, the Creator of all things. Glory be to Allah, the Creator of the seen and the unseen. Glory be to Allah as much as the ink of His Words. Glory be to Allah, the Lord of the worlds.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Paak hai Allah, jaan-daaro’n ka paiyda karne waala. Paak hai Allah, surat-gari karne (surat bana ne) waala. Paak hai Allah, tamaam maujoodaat mein jode (pair) bana ne waala. Paak hai Allah, roshni wa taariki ka paiyda karne waala. Paak hai Allah, daane aur beej ko cheerne waala. Paak hai Allah, sab cheezo’n ka paiyda karne waala. Paak hai Allah, dekhi an-dekhi cheezo’n ka paiyda karne waala. Paak hai Allah, apne kalemaat ko badha ne waala. Paak hai Allah, jahano ka Paalne waala.", "Urdu": "پاک ہے اللہ جان داروں کا پیدا کرنے والاپاک ہے اللہ صورت گری کرنے والا پاک ہے اللہ تمام موجودات میں جوڑے بنانے والا پاک ہے اللہ روشنی و تاریکی کا پیدا کرنے والا پاک ہے اللہ دانے اور بیج کو چیرنے والا پاک ہے اللہ سب چیزوں کا پیدا کرنے والا پاک ہے اللہ دیکھی اَن دیکھی چیزوں کا پیدا کرنے والا پاک ہے اللہ اپنے کلمات کو بڑھانے والا پاک ہے اللہ جہانوں کاپالنے والا۔", "RArabic": "SUBHAA-NAL LAAHE BAARE-IN NASAME, SUBHAA-NAL LAAHIL MO-SAWWE-RE, SUBHAA-NAL LAAHE KHAALE-QIL AZ-WAAJE KULLE-HAA, SUBHAA-NAL LAAHE JAA-E’LIZ ZOLO-MAATE WAN-NOORE, SUBHAA-NAL LAAHE FAALE-QIL HABBE WAN-NAWAA, SUBHAA-NAL LAAHE KHAALE-QE KULLE SHAIY-IN, SUBHAA-NAL LAAHE KHAALE-QE MAA YORAA WA MAA LAA YORAA, SUBHAA-NAL LAAHE ME-DAADA KALE-MAATE-HI, SUBHAA-NAL LAAHE RABBIL A’A-LAMEENA.", "ArabicText1": "سُبْحَانَ اللهِ بَارِئِ النَّسَمِ، سُبْحَانَ اللهِ الْمُصَوِّرِ، سُبْحَانَ اللهِ خَالِقِ الْاَزْوَاجِ كُلِّهَا، سُبْحَانَ اللهِ جَاعِلِ الظُّلُمَاتِ وَالنُّوْرِ، سُبْحَانَ اللهِ فَالِقِ الْحَبِّ وَالنَّوٰى، سُبْحَانَ اللهِ خَالِقِ كُلِّ شَيْ‏ءٍ، سُبْحَانَ اللهِ خَالِقِ مَا يُرٰى وَمَا لَا يُرٰى، سُبْحَانَ اللهِ مِدَادَ كَلِمَاتِهٖ۔ سُبْحَانَ اللهِ رَبِّ الْعَالَمِيْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "A